de.java2html.javasource
Class JavaSource

java.lang.Object
  de.java2html.javasource.JavaSource

public class JavaSource
extends java.lang.Object

This class represents java source code in a parsed, but still flat style. It contains the raw text along with an array of source type entries (JavaSourceType) for each character. JavaSource objects are created using the JavaSourceParser. A JavaSource object can be pretty-printed to HTML by using the JavaSource2HTMLConverter. For questions, suggestions, bug-reports, enhancement-requests etc. I may be contacted at: markus@jave.de The Java2html home page is located at: http://www.java2html.de
